embeds.title: About
embeds.description:
Welcome to **The Arctic Forest** Discord server, the official community server for Chiyeko, an AI-powered VTuber! We're excited to have you here as we embark on this journey together.

Here in **The Arctic Forest,** you'll find a friendly and supportive community that is dedicated to all things Chiyeko. From updates on her pre-debut status to discussions about her favorite games and activities, we have channels for everything related to Chiyeko and her VTuber journey.

footer.text: Thank you for joining The Arctic Forest, and we look forward to getting to know you better!
